text: Point Lumpatang () is a beach and cape located in West Tapalang subdistrict, Mamuju Regency, West Sulawesi. The cape is the westernmost point of Sulawesi.http://www.big.go.id/assets/download/Atlas-Administrasi/30-Peta- Wilayah-Prov-Sulbar.pdf The waters around the cape is rich in squids. ==References== Lumpatang
